This is one of my favorite food spots. I regularly order to-go food from them, and always get the chicken quesadilla. It’s so flavorful and delicious. I’ve also tried the half chicken, which the flavor is great on, juicy dark meat, crispy skin, a little dry on the white meat however. The Tortas look a little more like a sub, but the flavor and textures are on point. Make sure you get extra napkins!! Four stars for lack of ambiance to eat in and occasionally lacking service. Overall, best top five take out spots IMO.
